$(document).ready(function(){$("#sections").on("change",function(){const t=$(this).val();if(" "!==t){$(".loader img").show(),$("header").addClass("transform-head"),function(t){$.ajax({method:"GET",url:`https://api.nytimes.com/svc/topstories/v2/${t}.json?api-key=HtMSYIqpXwtwQGBCnI7l6BL1ypk4329Z`}).done(function(t){$(".loader img").hide(),$("ul").empty();let e=t.results.filter(function(t){return t.multimedia.length});e=e.slice(0,12);for(let t of e)$(".story").append(`<div class="article"> <a href=${t.url} target="_blank">\n                <li class="article-item" style='background: url(${t.multimedia[4].url});background-size:cover;'>\n                 <div class=stories-time><p>\n                    ${t.abstract}\n                    </p>\n                    </div>\n                    </li>\n                    </a>\n                    </div>`)}).fail(function(){$("ul").empty(),$("ul").append("<p>CLick harder!</p>")})}(t)}})});